":1500000240,"externalId":"4720285067001_2","objectType":"BUNDLE","isLive":false,"objectSubtype":"SEASON","contentType":"BUNDLE","contentSubtype":"SEASON","title":"Season 2","longDescription":"Ek Duje Ke Vaaste 2 is the love story of two people from different worlds. Shravan is an ambitious 18-year-old from a civilian family, while Suman is a disciplined 18-year-old girl from an Army family. Suman wishes to follow the family legacy and join the Indian Army one day to make her hero, her father and country proud. Shravan is the only son of a rich father, the apple of his mother's eye, raised with a lavish lifestyle. His aim is to fly out of the country as soon he finishes school. He thinks that civilians can have the same character and loyalty for the country as an Army person, while Suman believes in looking at everything from the lens of the Army lifestyle. Their worlds can't be more different. The civilian world where 'providing for the family' and 'earning good money' are the most important things. Whereas in the army world where gallantry, pride and honor are most important, and country comes before family. But, love as an emotion remains thesame with its countless colours and shades. Come and watch Suman and Shravan navigate their differences, fall in love, suffer heartbreak and betrayal, and meet again to fulfil their one destiny to be with each other.","shortDescription":"Ek Duje Ke Vaaste 2 is the love story of two people from different worlds. Shravan is an ambitious 18-year-old from a civilian family, while Suman is a disciplined 18-year-old girl from an Army family. Suman wishes to follow the family legacy and join the Indian Army one day to make her hero, her father and country proud. Shravan is the only son of a rich father, the apple of his mother's eye, raised with a lavish lifestyle. His aim is to fly out of the country as soon he finishes school. He thinks that civilians can have the same character and loyalty for the country as an Army person, while Suman believes in looking at everything from the lens of the Army lifestyle. Their worlds can't be more different. The civilian world where 'providing for the family' and 'earning good money' are the most important things. Whereas in the army world where gallantry, pride and honor are most important, and country comes before family. But, love as an emotion remains thesame with its countless colours and shades. Come and watch Suman and Shravan navigate their differences, fall in love, suffer heartbreak and betrayal, and meet again to fulfil their one destiny to be with each other.","contractStartDate":1575433740000,"contractEndDate":4705410540000,"episodeTitle":"","genres":["Romance"],"originalAirDate":1581292800000,"season":2,"pcExtendedRatings":[],"isOnAir":true,"isEncrypted":false,"pcVodLabel":"U/A 7+","duration":0,"language":"HIN","pictureUrl":"NA","advertisingInfoList":[],"emfAttributes":{"region_of_origin":"Hindi","audio_languages":"HIN","sub_category":"TV Show","snp_tags":"Romance,Family Drama","is_multi_track_per_language_available":false,"packageid":"12m_120_india,12mn_499_india,1m_Alliance_30,3m_120_india,3mn_149_india,6mn_199_india,JIO_SONYLIV_PREM,LIV_Pre_12M,liv_premium_amznbdl,LIV_Pre_1M,LIV_Pre_Sup_12M,liv_premium_ginirexgtouch_6m,liv_premium_ginirexgtouch_12m,liv_premium_dish_1m,liv_premium_mobikwik_1m,liv_premium_mobikwik_6m,liv_premium_mobikwik_12m,liv_premium_cahoots_1m,liv_premium_cahoots_6m,liv_premium_cahoots_12m,LIV_PRE_Mob_12M,liv_premium_plugandplay_1m,liv_premium_fino_1m,liv_premium_fino_6m,liv_premium_fino_12m,liv_premium_paynearby_1m,liv_premium_paynearby_6m,liv_premium_paynearby_12m,liv_premium_vi_post_unlimited_1m,liv_premium_aeoncom_1m,liv_premium_aeoncom_6m,liv_premium_aeoncom_12m,liv_premium_sonybravia_3m,liv_premium_udigital_12m,liv_premium_udigital_6m,liv_premium_htmedia_12m,liv_premium_htmedia_6m,liv_premium_redtv_12m,liv_premium_infynect_1m,liv_premium_buzzbites_1m,liv_premium_aeon_1m,liv_premium_aeon_6m,liv_premium_aeon_12m,liv_